headline: HVAC and Water Systems Stocks Q4 Earnings: Lennox (NYSE:LII) Firing on All Cylinders
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at hvac and water systems stocks, starting with Lennox (NYSE:LII).
